Econ.name: Meme Economy
Econ.description: Get it while its hot! This is a premade meme. You will not be able to make an modifications to it, but its price has been reduced!

Propane.name: Ascended Past Propane
Propane.description: A meme that originated from VR chat, and one that can't be modified. This meme describes the struggle of Hank Hill, a member of the Akatsuki trying to become god by ascending past all known sources of energy!

F.name: Press F To Pay Respects
F.description: This meme can be have text added to it to modify its contents! Anything you want to pay respects too, can be added. We will even throw in a free F key to simulate pushing the button.

Rick.name: Rick Roll
Rick.description: A classic, this meme can be yours for only $0.01! Add it to the back of a shirt to fool your friends.

Greed.name: Greedy Milk
Greed.description: The favored drink made from those with platinum to spare, send in any drinking contatiner to get it branded as a bottle of Greedy Milk, note it does not come with Grakatas.

9000.name: It's Over 9000
9000.price: Evidence that your Power Level is over 9000
9000.description: Show everyone how tough you are with this trophy.

Money.name: Take My Money
Money.description: You probably can't afford this, but on the off chance that you can, go ahead and show everyone how rich you are Mr. Moneybags!

ChairForce.name: Ugandan AirForce Tiger Mafia
ChairForce.description: Become the legendary Tiger Mafia Ugandan Airforce pilot yourself! You just need to be able to afford his helicopter.

Captain.name: Captain America Lecture
Captain.description: Behold as Captain America tells others what to do! When ordering this product, make sure to add what you want him to say!

Arrow.name: An Arrow to the Knee
Arrow.description: Show everyone that you were once an ex-adventurer with this product.
